## 🎉 **Get Started Today!**

```bash
# Install NextPy by RAHIMSTUDIOS
pip install nextpy-framework

# Create your first project
nextpy create my-awesome-app

# Start building amazing web applications with Python!
cd my-awesome-app && nextpy dev
```

